- Implement sliders for image settings
- Make QML load values available from the `Settings` classes
- Implement settings screens:
    - Base settings: 
        - Resolution: Dropdown
        - FPS: Dropdown depends on resolution
        - Orientation: Dropdown
    - Advanced Settings:
        - Stabilisation: Switch
        - Shutter speed: Dropdown
        - Exposure mode: Dropdown
        - Metering mode: Dropdown
    - Encoder Settings:
        - Keyframe interval: Slider
        - Bitrate: Slider, min == auto
        - QP: Slider
        - Preview Encoded: Switch
    - Streaming Settings:
        - Streaming Protocol: Dropdown
        - Streaming Target: URL
        - Stream key: Text
    - Recording Settings:
        - Location: Text
        - Split: Switch
        - Split size: Text (Number)
    - Audio Settings:
        - Enabled: Switch
        - Codec: Dropdown
        - Bitrate: Dropdown
        - Channels: Dropdown (Mono L, Mono R, Stereo)
- Implement histogram
- Implement audio Vu meters
- Implement audio volume